description:
Merchants that provide commercial art or graphic design services for
advertising agencies, publishers, and other businesses. Such services
may include silk screen design, still and slide film production, chart
and graph design, and commercial art and illustration.
For merchants that provide still, video, and portrait photography for
the general public, use MCC 7221.
